New Records: Kumar Rocker tied Don Stanhouse for second-most club history over their first two MLB appearances, with 12 strikeouts
Key Match Events: Kumar Rocker struggled with his command and velocity, allowing two runs (one earned) on two hits and four walks, while striking out five in three innings
Pre-Game Insights: Kumar Rocker had Tommy John surgery in May 2023 after being the No. 3 overall pick in the 2022 MLB Draft
Post-Match Reflections: Manager Bruce Bochy cut off Rocker's pitch count at 60, which is where he would be cut off
Miscellaneous Highlights: Kumar Rocker's home debut at Globe Life Field was marked by struggles with command and velocity
Others: Rocker threw 71 pitches, including 41 strikes, and left the game trailing 2-0
